universum.studios.android.ui.interpolator

Class ResistanceInterpolator

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.ui.interpolator.ResistanceInterpolator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeInterpolator, Interpolator

    public class ResistanceInterpolator
extends Object
implements Interpolator
    Implementation of Interpolator to provide "resistance" like behaviour. Resistance interpolation is simulated a way, where the bigger input is the bigger is resistance.

    Interpolation equation

    input * Math.max((1 - input), minResistanceFactor)
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
